Cell["\<\
The following general method is simpler to implement but also \"naive\" in \
the sense that it uses the default inefficient version of Outer. Then it can \
be used as a method for testing the more sophisticated efficient \
implementation with monotonicOuter.\
\>", "Text",
 TaggingRules-><|
