   3.981446598461873*^9, 3.98144673636204*^9}, {3.981447336772451*^9, 
   3.981447390922814*^9}, 
   3.9814761561987305`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"aa3d593d-7147-4461-a761-\
78fa64d0389e"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "As it happens for resource function \"",
 ButtonBox["AlgebraicRange",
  BaseStyle->"Hyperlink",
  ButtonData->{
    URL["https://resources.wolframcloud.com/FunctionRepository/resources/\
AlgebraicRange"], None},
  ButtonNote->
   "https://resources.wolframcloud.com/FunctionRepository/resources/\
AlgebraicRange"],
 "\", also the definition of ",
 Cell[BoxData["TranscendentalRange"], "InlineFormula",
  FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
  "d6d1fc2d-8b7d-4a8a-9bee-03b4f4ba2d42"],
 " allows the user to specify a fourth argument ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["d", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "44641863-ddda-46cf-95be-9b1e05205321"],
 ", to require a minimum absolute value ",
 ButtonBox["difference",
  BaseStyle->"Link",
  ButtonData->"paclet:ref/Differences"],
 " between successive transcendentals and thus avoid the tendency to produce \
very irregular distributions of numeric values."
}], "Notes",
 TaggingRules->{},
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.981446683220306*^9, 3.981446687175537*^9}, {
  3.981446776770034*^9, 3.9814470941121492`*^9}, {3.9814765929676743`*^9, 
  3.981476608553072*^9}, {3.981476643461502*^9, 
  3.9814766926354465`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"6f281874-26f3-43b6-aac8-\
9238bc0b1c86"],

Cell[TextData[{
 Cell[BoxData["TranscendentalRange"], "InlineFormula",
  FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
  "c58e394d-a97c-406a-bc62-bf81376702f2"],
 " has been designed especially in view of its application to the resource \
function  \"",
 ButtonBox["FindClosedForm",
  BaseStyle->"Hyperlink",
  ButtonData->{
    URL["https://resources.wolframcloud.com/FunctionRepository/resources/\
FindClosedForm"], None},
  ButtonNote->
   "https://resources.wolframcloud.com/FunctionRepository/resources/\
FindClosedForm"],
 "\" for exhaustively searching possible closed forms for raw numbers in \
terms of arbitrary mathematical functions with transcendental arguments."
}], "Notes",
