Cell["\<\
For all these transcendental types, the generated exact numbers have been \
mathematically proven to be transcendental through the theorems of \
Lindemann-Weierstrass, Gelfond-Schneider and Baker (cf. Baker, 1975).\
\>", "Notes",
 TaggingRules-><|
  "ChatNotebookSettings" -> <|
    "InheritanceTest" -> True, 
     "ServiceDefaultModel" -> <|
