Cell["\<\
Actually, this first version implements only a minimal subset of all possible \
expressions which these theorems prove to be transcendental numbers. I hope \
to implement also more general possibilities and a more efficient algorithm \
in later versions.\
\>", "Text",
 TaggingRules->{},
 InitializationCell->True,
